Description: EKF System Management Library
 The EKF System Management Library (ekfsm) is a sensor monitoring suite
 for Compact PCI Serial devices. It provides comprehensive monitoring
 and control capabilities for embedded systems.
 .
 This package includes all dependencies bundled in a highly compressed
 format with locked versions for deployment-ready single-artifact
 distribution.
